  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/17e7aed824d5a7d6a14dcce409daa52d.avif?t=1725519295\" width=532 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/61789780c20863bd31b9e96402492fb1.avif?t=1725519295\" width=225 height=267 /></span><br>Travel through Rainbow Lands as Bitsy, a Magiforma Magimouse, to defeat Twinkle, another Magimouse surrounded by hordes of characters that playfully (and sometimes lazily) try to stop you on your way there. There's plenty of sights to see and magic to try as you bounce your way through this unforgettable adventure!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/52cb09fee6f65f368053a7b9b7e929ea.avif?t=1725519295\" width=454 height=256 /></span><br><strong>Objective</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play as Bitsy<br></li><li> Travel to each castle by getting through each stage to defeat Twinkle<br></li><li> Clear each stage by bouncing away characters that stand in your way<br></li><li> Find magic to help you on your journey</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/14231ff9226efd31b7223f9021b8d1f9.avif?t=1725519295\" width=480 height=250 /></span><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>60+ stages, 30+ \"Magican\" magic, 120+ variations of magic<br></li><li>Wonderful cast of characters<br></li><li>Xbox pc controller supported and preferred<br></li><li>In game option to play with the computer mouse only, the most unique way to play the game!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/cf181a5d224e3487ad40c43658e5698f.webp?t=1725519295\" width=106 height=60 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/17e7aed824d5a7d6a14dcce409daa52d.avif?t=1725519295\" width=532 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/61789780c20863bd31b9e96402492fb1.avif?t=1725519295\" width=225 height=267 /></span><br>Travel through Rainbow Lands as Bitsy, a Magiforma Magimouse, to defeat Twinkle, another Magimouse surrounded by hordes of characters that playfully (and sometimes lazily) try to stop you on your way there. There's plenty of sights to see and magic to try as you bounce your way through this unforgettable adventure!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/52cb09fee6f65f368053a7b9b7e929ea.avif?t=1725519295\" width=454 height=256 /></span><br><strong>Objective</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play as Bitsy<br></li><li> Travel to each castle by getting through each stage to defeat Twinkle<br></li><li> Clear each stage by bouncing away characters that stand in your way<br></li><li> Find magic to help you on your journey</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/14231ff9226efd31b7223f9021b8d1f9.avif?t=1725519295\" width=480 height=250 /></span><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>60+ stages, 30+ \"Magican\" magic, 120+ variations of magic<br></li><li>Wonderful cast of characters<br></li><li>Xbox pc controller supported and preferred<br></li><li>In game option to play with the computer mouse only, the most unique way to play the game!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093960/extras/cf181a5d224e3487ad40c43658e5698f.webp?t=1725519295\" width=106 height=60 /></span>",
